00:22:54,231 --> 00:22:59,236
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

316
00:22:59,862 --> 00:23:01,447
<font color="japanese">（天城）困った人ですね</c.japanese>

317
00:23:01,572 --> 00:23:03,157
<font color="japanese">これから少し会えますか？</c.japanese>

318
00:23:03,282 --> 00:23:05,201
<font color="japanese">（冴）何で そんなに
佐藤さんがいいの？</c.japanese>

319
00:23:05,326 --> 00:23:07,077
<font color="japanese">（藍田）俺 佐藤さんのことが…</c.japanese>

320
00:23:07,536 --> 00:23:09,622
<font color="japanese">（冴）あっちもこっちも
佐藤さん 佐藤さんて…</c.japanese>

321
00:23:09,747 --> 00:23:10,581
<font color="japanese">なんかムカつく</c.japanese>

322
00:23:10,706 --> 00:23:14,251
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（男性）</c.japanese>
